{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales_marketing", "channel": "market_analysis", "user": "john_doe", "message": "Hi team, let's not forget about the quarterly market trends presentation next week. I expect everyone to be prepared with their respective slides.", "created_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales_marketing", "channel": "market_analysis", "user": "emily_lee", "message": "Sure, John. I will share the latest updates on competitors' marketing strategies. I'll also need some data from the sales team.", "created_at": 1620501000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "customer_relations", "channel": "customer_retention", "user": "jane_smith", "message": "Reminder - we have a meeting with the technical team tomorrow to discuss the new customer service platform. Please come with your feedback and suggestions.", "created_at": 1620502000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales_marketing", "channel": "market_analysis", "user": "john_doe", "message": "Emily, let's set up a meeting to discuss the data you need. Also, how is the preparation for the annual automotive trade show coming along?", "created_at": 1620503000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "customer_relations", "channel": "customer_retention", "user": "emily_lee", "message": "Jane, I have been reviewing the features of the new platform and I think it could really help us improve our response times. Looking forward to the meeting tomorrow.", "created_at": 1620504000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales_marketing", "channel": "market_analysis", "user": "emily_lee", "message": "John, the trade show preparation is going well. We are finalizing the list of products for display. Let's discuss more in our meeting.", "created_at": 1620505000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "customer_relations", "channel": "customer_retention", "user": "jane_smith", "message": "Emily, glad to hear your feedback on the new platform. Let's discuss more in the meeting tomorrow. We need to make sure it's well integrated with our current systems.", "created_at": 1620506000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales_marketing", "channel": "market_analysis", "user": "john_doe", "message": "Looking forward to our meeting, Emily. Let's ensure we make a strong impact at the trade show this year.", "created_at": 1620507000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales_marketing", "channel": "market_analysis", "user": "john_doe", "message": "Team, we've been discussing ways to increase engagement with second-hand buyers of our EVs. I believe leveraging Automotive Cloud's vehicle tracking capabilities could be a significant step forward. However, we currently lack a systematic way to track the ownership changes among our second-hand buyers. Thoughts?", "create_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales_marketing", "channel": "market_analysis", "user": "emily_lee", "message": "John, you're absolutely right. We do have a gap in our data collection when it comes to second-hand buyers. As of now, we don't have any system integrated with U.S. DMV databases to track vehicle ownership changes. This makes identifying and reaching out to second-hand buyers quite challenging through our current channels.", "create_at": 1620500005000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales_marketing", "channel": "market_analysis", "user": "john_doe", "message": "Thanks for confirming, Emily. We definitely need to consider a solution that helps us track these changes and engage with the second-hand buyers more effectively. Let's explore how we can leverage Automotive Cloud in this regard.", "create_at": 1620500010000}}
